#~ "--Velitel Navarre"

#, fuzzy
#~ msgid ""
#~ "This is one of several proposals I'm submitting for the research and "
#~ "development of new laser weaponry. Each of these will have to be "
#~ "developed separately due to the size differences, power levels and "
